Distribution. Indian Ocean: Mauritius ( Haller 1880 ; Bruce 1986 ), Zanzibar ( Pfeffer 1889 ; Bruce 1986 ), Indonesia ( Nierstrasz 1915 ; Bruce 1986 ), India ( Nair 1950 ; Pillai 1954 ;
Gopalakrishnan et al. 2010
;
Ravichandran et al. 2011
; Trilles et al. 2011; Sethi et al. 2013; Rameshkumar et al. 2014;
